<subSubSection id="02C66578FFF8FFB9FC959A4C6A7E7BBF" pageId="21" pageNumber="35" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="4A6336F3FFF8FFB9FC959A4C6DB97B21" blockId="21.[831,1437,1544,1758]" pageId="21" pageNumber="35">
<emphasis id="78A8EAE1FFF8FFB9FC959A4C6ABD7B41" bold="true" box="[831,944,1544,1568]" pageId="21" pageNumber="35">Remarks:</emphasis>
It is characterized by projecting nodes of variable distribution and elevation.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="4A6336F3FFF8FFB9FC959A0C6A7E7BBF" blockId="21.[831,1437,1544,1758]" pageId="21" pageNumber="35">
<emphasis id="78A8EAE1FFF8FFB9FC959A0C6D707B01" bold="true" box="[831,1149,1608,1632]" pageId="21" pageNumber="35">Stratigraphic distribution:</emphasis>
It is recorded in the Paleocene sediments (BERGGREN &amp; AUBERT, 1975 and LE ROY, 1953). It is recorded in the Late Paleocene 
<emphasis id="78A8EAE1FFF8FFB9FC959AE36A4A7BDE" box="[831,839,1703,1727]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="35">(</emphasis>
<taxonomicName id="8DDC4D70FFF8FFB9FCED9AE36D967BDE" authority="Zone" authorityName="Zone" box="[839,1179,1703,1727]" class="Globothalamea" family="Truncorotaloididae" genus="Morozovella" kingdom="Chromista" order="Rotaliida" pageId="21" pageNumber="35" phylum="Foraminifera" rank="species" species="velascoensis">
<emphasis id="78A8EAE1FFF8FFB9FCED9AE36D517BDE" box="[839,1116,1703,1727]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="35">Morozovella velascoensis</emphasis>
Zone
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis id="78A8EAE1FFF8FFB9FB319AEC6DA97BDE" box="[1179,1188,1704,1727]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="35">)</emphasis>
of the Esh El Mallaha area.
</paragraph>
